data.description: This Charming two-story home is located within the Way Station Subdivision. Built by JM Allen Homes. Make your way through the foyer to a bright spacious family room that is great for entertaining. In the kitchen, you will observe the beautiful granite countertops, backsplash, cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and breakfast area. Head upstairs and see the spacious master suite that includes a walk-in closet; a master bath with double vanity, garden tub, and separate shower. You will find three additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a laundry room upstairs. Large backyard with a covered patio and fire pit. Love what you see? Call us today to schedule your private showing!
